Double Punch/Punch/Hiss:



Double Punch ducked, the rockets passing over his head, exploding against a 
few trees, starting a small fire.  The nearly cloaked Predacon slammed a 
pincher on the ground, the limb opening, a missile firing off at Hot Rod.

--

Punch screamed, flying back through the air, slamming through a tree, not 
getting up, though not in stasis lock.

---

Hiss cursed, firing off three fusion blasts at Hot Rod.
